<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Those newbie killers on PVP server</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Draknoir">Draknoir</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 6:17 p.m. 12/2/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Those newbie killers on PVP server<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR></STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>Someone posted a message on the PVP EQ server suggesting no pvp for people below level 3 (I think) because a group of players was killing newbies in the bat yards. Post names of these people so the general population can go take care of them. Their actions only hurt the entire PVP community as they chase people out of the PVP game by killing them repeatedly for no reason. PVP people that server is yours.. defend it from idiots who try to ruin it.

<P>This is exactly the type of thing we were talking about near the end of phase 3.5 - if players step up against this kind of action the PVP world will be a much better place for all.
<P>Drak
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
